    <div class="col_one_third bottommargin-sm center">
      <img data-animate="fadeInLeft" src="<%= asset_path 'HowItWorks_Step_2.jpg' %>" alt="Step 1">
    </div>
    <div class="col_two_third bottommargin-sm col_last">
      <div class="heading-block">
        <h3>Shop</h3>
      </div>
      <p>
        Give us some basic info and we’ll show you all the loan programs that you qualify for from several wholesale lenders on our platform. Our rate quotes include full breakdown of third-party fees and our True Cost of Mortgage algorithm can recommend the best mortgage for your scenario.
